=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains the delivery stream Amazon Resource Name (ARN), and the ARN of
the Identity and Access Management (IAM) role associated with a
Firehose event destination.

Event destinations, such as Firehose, are associated with configuration
sets, which enable you to publish message sending events.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> DeliveryStreamArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the delivery stream.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> IamRoleArn => Str

The ARN of an Identity and Access Management role that is able to write
event data to an Amazon Data Firehose destination.



